        <version>1.0.0</version>
        <title>Clean Architecture API Template</title>
        <authors>Stiven Bohorquez</authors>
        
        <description>
            This API template provides a solid foundation for developing applications using a hexagonal architecture. 
            It includes JWT authentication to ensure secure communication, exception handling for efficient error management, 
            and configurable CORS policies for cross-domain request handling. Additionally, it integrates database connections 
            to facilitate data access and persistence. This template is designed to enable developers to focus on business 
            logic from the outset, providing a clear and maintainable structure for building robust and scalable APIs.
        </description>
        
        <summary>
            A starter template for building APIs with a hexagonal architecture, featuring JWT authentication, exception handling, 
            configurable CORS policies, and database connectivity. Ideal for developers looking to quickly implement 
            business logic in a structured and maintainable environment.
        </summary>

